init_he = tf.keras.initializers.HeNormal()

model_dense = tf.keras.models.Sequential([
                                     
    # tf.keras.layers.Flatten(input_shape=(513,1)),
    tf.keras.layers.Input(shape=(513,)),
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(1024 , activation="relu", kernel_initializer=init_he, name='layer1'),
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(1024, activation="relu", kernel_initializer=init_he, name='layer2'),
    
    tf.keras.layers.Dense(513, activation='sigmoid', name='output_layer')
    # tf.keras.layers.Reshape((513, 2459), input_shape=(513*2459,))
    ])
opt_adam = keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=0.001)
model_dense.compile(
  optimizer=opt_adam,
  
  # loss=tf.losses.SparseCategoricalCrossentropy(from_logits=True),
  loss='msle',
  metrics=['accuracy'])
